<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>Or if they were dark cells, it was like iron</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691000' id='t-691000'>corrugated, and he would put his fingers through.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
