</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693000' id='t-693000'>And most of the prisoners said that he was</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>their greatest joy and their sunshine, and they</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>looked forward to him. And I was like,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699000' id='t-699000'>here's Vishna. He's a 4-year-old boy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701000' id='t-701000'>He was born in a prison with almost nothing,</span>
